";s:3:"row";i:3;s:3:"col";i:4;s:4:"isrm";i:1;s:10:"ddmaxwidth";i:200;s:10:"pagepicnum";i:12;s:7:"templet";s:0:"";s:6:"userip";s:9:"127.0.0.1";s:11:"redirecturl";s:0:"";s:4:"body";s:4586:"<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, times, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, PMingLiU, PMingLiu-ExtB, SimSun, SimSun-ExtB, HanaMinA, HanaMinB; font-size: 18.6667px; text-size-adjust: auto;">原宪居鲁，环堵之室，茨以蒿莱，蓬户瓮牖，桷桑而无枢，上漏下湿，匡坐而弦歌。子贡乘肥马，衣轻裘，中绀而表素，轩不容巷，而往见之。原宪楮冠黎杖而应门，正冠则缨绝，振襟则肘见，纳履则踵决。子贡曰：&ldquo;嘻！先生何病也！&rdquo;原宪仰而应之曰：&ldquo;宪闻之：无财之谓贫，学而不能行之谓病。宪、贫也，非病也。若夫希世而行，比周而友，学以为人，教以为己，仁义之匿，车马之饰，衣裘之丽，宪不忍为之也。&rdquo;子贡逡巡，面有惭色，不辞而去。原宪乃徐步曳杖，歌商颂而反，声沦于天地，如出金石。天子不得而臣也，诸侯不得而友也。故养身者忘家，养志者忘身，身且不爱，孰能忝之。《</span><a class="popup" href="https://ctext.org/book-of-poetry/zhs" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, times, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, PMingLiU, PMingLiu-ExtB, SimSun, SimSun-ExtB, HanaMinA, HanaMinB; font-size: 18.6667px; text-size-adjust: auto;">诗</a><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, times, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, PMingLiU, PMingLiu-ExtB, SimSun, SimSun-ExtB, HanaMinA, HanaMinB; font-size: 18.6667px; text-size-adjust: auto;">》曰：&ldquo;</span><a class="popup" href="https://ctext.org/book-of-poetry/bo-zhou/zhs?searchu=%E6%88%91%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%AA%E7%9F%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%BD%89%E4%B9%9F%EF%BC%9B%E6%88%91%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%AA%E5%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B7%E4%B9%9F%E3%80%82&amp;searchmode=showall#result" rel="nofollow" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, times, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, PMingLiU, PMingLiu-ExtB, SimSun, SimSun-ExtB, HanaMinA, HanaMinB; font-size: 18.6667px; text-size-adjust: auto;">我心匪石，不可转也；我心匪席，不可卷也。</a><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, times, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, PMingLiU, PMingLiu-ExtB, SimSun, SimSun-ExtB, HanaMinA, HanaMinB; font-size: 18.6667px; text-size-adjust: auto;">&rdquo;<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />
<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />
<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />
<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-size-adjust: auto;">原宪居鲁，环堵之室，茨以蒿莱，蓬户瓮牖，桷桑而无枢，上漏下湿，匡坐而弦歌。子贡乘肥马，衣轻裘，中绀而表素，轩不容巷，而往见之。原宪楮冠黎杖而应门，正冠则缨绝，振襟则肘见，纳履则踵决。子贡曰：&ldquo;嘻！先生何病也！&rdquo;原宪仰而应之曰：&ldquo;宪闻之：无财之谓贫，学而不能行之谓病。宪、贫也，非病也。若夫希世而行，比周而友，学以为人，教以为己，仁义之匿，车马之饰，衣裘之丽，宪不忍为之也。&rdquo;子贡逡巡，面有惭色，不辞而去。原宪乃徐步曳杖，歌商颂而反，声沦于天地，如出金石。天子不得而臣也，诸侯不得而友也。故养身者忘家，养志者忘身，身且不爱，孰能忝之。《</span><a class="popup" href="https://ctext.org/book-of-poetry/zhs" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; text-size-adjust: auto;">诗</a><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-size-adjust: auto;">》曰：&ldquo;</span><a class="popup" href="https://ctext.org/book-of-poetry/bo-zhou/zhs?searchu=%E6%88%91%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%AA%E7%9F%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%BD%89%E4%B9%9F%EF%BC%9B%E6%88%91%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%AA%E5%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B7%E4%B9%9F%E3%80%82&amp;searchmode=showall#result" rel="nofollow" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; text-size-adjust: auto;">我心匪石，不可转也；我心匪席，不可卷也。</a><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-size-adjust: auto;">&rdquo;</span></span>";s:3:"url";s:32:"/index/template/view/aid/68.html";}}s:4:"page";N;s:8:"template";s:22:"{style}/list_image.htm";s:8:"typename";s:6:"图集";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:6:"&nbsp;";}